2014-08-03  Mike Frysinger  <vapier@gentoo.org>

  * src/cmd/Makefile.am: Switch generated_cmd_list.h to BUILT_SOURCES rather
    than creating the dependency ourselves between the objects.

  * src/bus/buses_list.h: Add mpc8313 as reported by Greg Foringer.

  * data/Makefile.am, data/xilinx/PARTS, data/xilinx/xc2vp4/STEPPINGS,
    data/xilinx/xc2vp4/xc2vp4: Add xc2vp4 (Virtex II Pro FPGA) details by
    Michael Davidsaver.

  * data/xilinx/xcf08p/STEPPINGS: Add rev 14 by Michael Davidsaver.

  * src/cmd/Makefile.am: Fix generated_cmd_list.h generation so it always
    includes all commands and not just ones enabled by configure.  Reported
    by Nick B.

2014-08-01  Mike Frysinger  <vapier@gentoo.org>

  * data/xilinx/PARTS, data/xilinx/xc7a100t/STEPPINGS,
    data/xilinx/xc7a100t/xc7a100t-csg324: Add xilinx Artix-7 part info by
    Steve Tell.

2014-07-29  Mike Frysinger  <vapier@gentoo.org>

  * configure.ac: Enable subdir-objects as latest automake warns otherwise.
    Switch the dist tarball to xz while we're here.

2014-07-29  Mike Frysinger  <vapier@gentoo.org>

  * src/bsdl/bsdl_bison.y, src/bsdl/vhdl_bison.y, src/svf/svf_bison.y: Deploy
    a hack to work around limitations in the new %lex-param interface.
    Debugging by Paul Green & cioma in sourceforge bug 118.

2014-07-29  Mike Frysinger  <vapier@gentoo.org>

  * src/bus/h7202.c: Fix max number of lines setup to match struct.

2014-01-18  Mike Frysinger  <vapier@gentoo.org>

  * src/bsdl/bsdl_bison.y, src/bsdl/vhdl_bison.y, src/svf/svf_bison.y: Define
    %lex-param to fix building with bison-3+; fix by Daniel Burr.  Also update
    %name-prefix to avoid build time warnings.  This breaks building w/older
    bison versions like 1.875d, but bison-2.0 was released in 2005.

2013-05-08  Mike Frysinger  <vapier@gentoo.org>

  * configure.ac: Update to autoconf 2.64 and gettext 0.17.

2013-03-26  Mike Frysinger  <vapier@gentoo.org>

  * configure.ac: Change AM_CONFIG_HEADER to AC_CONFIG_HEADERS to fix
    warnings from newer automake.
  * src/Makefile.am, src/apps/bsdl2jtag/Makefile.am, src/apps/jtag/Makefile.am:
    Change INCLUDES to AM_CPPFLAGS to fix warnings from newer automake.

2013-03-24  Mike Frysinger  <vapier@gentoo.org>

  * configure.ac: Check for libftdi1 with newer releases.

