   * src/bus/bf561_ezkit.c (bf561_ezkit_bus_new): Likewise.
   * src/bus/s3c4510x.c (s3c4510_bus_new): Likewise.
   * src/bus/ejtag.c (ejtag_bus_new): Likewise.
