   * configure.ac: check for pre-generated src/svf/svf_flex.c
       -> second part of [ 1895353 ]
   * src/bsdl/Makefile.am (noinst_HEADERS): bsdl_sysdep.h added for proper
       release packing -> first part of [ 1895353 ]

